{
  "stem": "25651.11",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Herting told me that the people in the SS who are in the command of looking after prisoners are themselves prisoners, because they will never do anything else except work with prisoners.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because this is all secret.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the only way that they can get out of this prison detail is to volunteer for the front.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this Von Schwartzenberg volunteered for the front rather than stay in some sort of sinecure in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, once more.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, my portrait is painted over another two or three weeks, through August.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there's a fire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the man-- the painter-- put a light to all the paints and he burned everything and committed suicide in the fire.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this sort of topsy-turvy logic, you know, of this camp-- every barrack had a fire extinguisher.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the command is called from the gate-- every barrack, you know, fire extinguishers to the fire.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Nitka grabs the fire extinguisher and carries it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I run with Nitka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, fire, it's an event, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our scharfuhrer, the fellow who by-- by now had cut-- cut the swathe through my slowly-growing hair, is running behind us to the fire.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Nitka, poor chap-- I told you he was like a thread; he wasn't very strong-- he hands me the fire extinguisher and he says, I can't anymore.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You-- you run with the fire extinguisher.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was a small boy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was a big thing, this fire extinguisher, and heavy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I couldn't carry it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I ran a few steps and then I slung it over my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] What I didn't know was that this was one of these fire extinguishers that you-- when you put it upside down, it activates.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was running--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
